    "help_body": "<h2>How to Play</h2><div style=\"text-align:center;margin:12px 0\"><div style=\"display:inline-grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,22px);gap:2px\"><div style=\"background:#888;border-radius:3px;height:22px\"></div><div style=\"background:#3498db;border-radius:3px;height:22px\"></div><div style=\"background:#3498db;border-radius:3px;height:22px\"></div><div style=\"background:#e74c3c;border-radius:3px;height:22px\"></div><div style=\"background:#f1c40f;border-radius:3px;height:22px\"></div><div style=\"background:#1a1a40;border-radius:3px;height:22px;border:1px solid #333\"></div><div style=\"background:#888;border-radius:3px;height:22px\"></div><div style=\"background:#e74c3c;border-radius:3px;height:22px\"></div><div style=\"background:#ecf0f1;border-radius:3px;height:22px\"></div><div style=\"background:#ecf0f1;border-radius:3px;height:22px\"></div><div style=\"background:#f1c40f;border-radius:3px;height:22px\"></div><div style=\"background:#888;border-radius:3px;height:22px\"></div></div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#666;margin-top:4px\">Grey = fixed · Colored = yours to place</div></div><p><strong>Goal:</strong> Fill every cell on the 8×8 board using 11 tiles. 3 grey tiles are pre-placed — arrange the remaining 8.</p><h3>🎯 Basic Controls</h3><ul><li><strong>Place</strong> — Drag a tile from the tray onto the board, or tap to select then tap a cell.</li><li><strong>Rotate</strong> — Tap a selected tile again to rotate 90°.</li><li><strong>Remove</strong> — Drag a placed tile off the board, or tap it to pick it back up.</li></ul><h3>⭐ Grades &amp; Rewards</h3><p>Every solve earns a grade and EXP:</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong style=\"color:#f1c40f\">S</strong> Under par + no hints (×2 EXP) · <strong style=\"color:#2ecc71\">A</strong> Fast or no hints (×1.5) · <strong style=\"color:#3498db\">B</strong> Completed (×1)</p><h3>💡 Hints &amp; ⚡ Energy</h3><ul><li><strong>3 free hints/day</strong> — extra hints cost 100💎. Using hints blocks S-rank.</li><li><strong>First puzzle daily is free</strong> — then 1⚡ per puzzle. Recovers 1 every 2h (max 5).</li></ul><h3>📋 Daily Tasks &amp; 💎 Multiplier</h3><p>Complete 3 daily tasks for diamond rewards. Earn 2× or 3× diamond buffs during happy hours or A+ streaks.</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:12px\"><a href=\"#\" onclick=\"window.open('help.html');return false\" style=\"color:#3498db;font-weight:600\">Full Guide →</a></p>",
